From: Jacob Sirotkin <jake.sirotkin@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 12:27:00 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add RE Taxes tab for co-ops with NYC DOF data integration

Adds a new RE Taxes tab to the FA budget dashboard for co-op buildings.
The tab auto-fetches assessed values and tax rates from NYC DOF (with
hardcoded fallback), renders a calculation layout with editable inputs
(light blue) and computed outputs (light green), and saves overrides
back to Gen & Admin GL lines.

- New module: dof_taxes.py (BBL lookup, tax computation, DOF API client)
- GET/PUT /api/re-taxes/<entity_code> endpoints
- renderRETaxesTab() JS with live recalculation
- Condos/rentals: tab hidden (co-ops only)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
